How to devalue the dollarTrump and Lighthizer want to "weaken" the dollar. It's an idea worth considering, but the devil is in the details. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-to-devalue-the-dollar https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-to-devalue-the-dollarNoah Smith Fri, 24 May 2024 21:02:21 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg" width="718" height="538.5" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:768,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:718,&quot;bytes&quot;:256633,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F33cc74b7-4d50-4f9b-9d6e-4a14c29f05ab_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> “<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/59937401@N07/5857169353">一美元钞票切成两半</a>”，作者： <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/59937401@N07">Images_of_Money</a> ， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/?ref=openverse">CC BY 2.0</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>有一天，我和一位政客（匿名）聊天，他告诉我他对中国有多么担心。我们讨论了战争风险，以及因中国竞争而失去的制造业工作岗位。但随后他说了一句出人意料的话。 “我认为他们的最终目标，”他阴沉地嘀咕道，“是压低美元汇率。”</p><p>我稍后会讨论这个想法，但真正令我震惊的是，许多美国人本能地将其货币的强势与国家的实力联系起来。我不太确定为什么。这可能只是对“力量”一词的不幸误解。事实上，美元“强势”只是一个口语术语——意思是美元相对于其他货币来说<em>昂贵</em>。或者，人们可能会意识到，当美国经济表现良好时，美元往往会走强，并假设相关性等于因果性。或者也许美国人只是为世界上有多少人想要持有本国货币而感到自豪。</p><p>不管出于什么原因，我认识两个人，他们认为“强势”美元不是一个好主意：唐纳德·特朗普和他的主要贸易顾问罗伯特·莱特希泽。 <a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2024/05/18/robert-lighthizer-trump-election-trade-tariffs-treasury-secretary/">特朗普承诺，如果他重新上任，将削弱美元</a>，而莱特希泽似乎是提出这一想法的人：</p><blockquote><p>莱特希泽本人一直在建议特朗普，如果他当选，就让<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2024/04/15/devaluing-dollar-trump-trade-war-00152009#:~:text=Advisers%20close%20to%20the%20former,exports%20but%20also%20fuel%20inflation.">强势美元贬值</a>，以促进美国出口——这一建议被广泛解读为财政部职位的试镜……</p><p> [莱特希泽]将把平衡与世界其他地区的贸易作为美国政策的目标，而不仅仅是与中国。其影响是巨大的。<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/2024/04/15/devaluing-dollar-trump-trade-war-00152009">据报道，莱特希泽向特朗普提出</a>的一项工具是共同努力削弱美元兑其他货币的汇率。在其他条件相同的情况下，美元贬值将降低外国人为美国出口产品支付的价格，使美国人的进口产品更加昂贵，并有助于使贸易更加接近平衡。然而，美元长期以来一直被高估，部分原因是其作为全球首选货币的角色。最近，由于美国经济强劲以及中东和欧洲的冲突，促使投资者纷纷涌向美国资产的避风港，该指数一直在飙升。细节很少，但莱特希泽似乎正在设想美国总统理查德·尼克松 (Richard Nixon) 和罗纳德·里根 (Ronald Reagan) 在 1971 年和 1987 年采取的行动的重演：对贸易伙伴征收或威胁征收关税，除非他们同意采取措施调整其货币兑美元汇率。</p></blockquote><p>这对全球金融体系和美国经济来说都是一个巨大的变化。这并不意味着这将是一个<em>糟糕的</em>改变。莱特希泽说得对，美元在某种程度上“疲软”可能会让美国出口在世界市场上更具竞争力，并有助于美国经济重新平衡，转向制造业，远离金融业。从长远来看，它可能有助于稳定全球金融体系。</p><p>但也存在很多危险。美元贬值几乎肯定会加剧通胀。它也很容易超调——<em>太</em>便宜的美元会让需要进口零部件和材料的美国制造商的日子变得更加艰难。美国可以用来让美元贬值的大多数方法要么有效性值得怀疑，要么可能会给金融体系带来严重问题。</p><p>无论如何，这是特朗普最大、最重要的经济提案——迄今为止比关税还要大。所以我想我应该写一篇关于整个问题的解释——为什么美元首先“坚挺”，“坚挺”美元的成本和收益，美元可能如何贬值，以及这对美国人意味着什么并为世界。</p><h4>基础知识：为什么美元“坚挺”，以及这对美国人意味着什么</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-to-devalue-the-dollar">阅读更多</a></p>;
How liberal democracy might lose the 21st centuryA scary little theory about information and freedom. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-liberal-democracy-might-lose https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-liberal-democracy-might-loseNoah Smith Wed, 22 May 2024 21:49:31 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg" width="1200" height="578" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ba726358-dce3-4784-82a3-5c71fbb1ca03_1200x578.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quo