式生活，买卖你想要的东西的自由——才是<em>胜利的关键</em>。</p><p>仅仅二十年后，这个想法就受到了严重质疑。民主化和社会自由化的浪潮<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-darkness">出现逆转</a>。美国社会和政治混乱四分五裂，制造业和住宅建设的弱点暴露无遗。与此同时，在习近平的领导下，21世纪初<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/china-at-the-peak">崛起的超级大国</a>中国又<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-governing-china-after-the-boom/?sref=R8NfLgwS">回到了</a>更加独裁的经济和更加极权的社会。</p><p>我认识的一些最近去中国旅行的人回来后都对中国与美国相比有多么美好的幻想： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F598ab4db-2e5a-4850-b29a-9511471f7c8e_656x839.jpeg" width="656" height="839" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;