3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://networkcontagion.us/wp-content/uploads/A-Tik-Tok-ing-Timebomb_12.21.23.pdf">NCRI/Rutgers</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这主要只是对美国人观点的无声审查制度。美国Tiktok用户甚至没有意识到这正在发生，因此不太可能使他们在互联网上的体验更加负面。但是随着时间的流逝，蒂克托克（Tiktok）在美国促进<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2024/01/08/china-antisemitism-online-tool-west-gaza/">分裂态度</a>可能会感染人类的​​意见，从而使互联网比以前更加极端和喊叫。</p><p>当然，总是有演员试图用虚假信息，影响运营等垃圾邮件垃圾邮件 - 公司，政党，利益集团等。但是，中国和俄罗斯的政府比其他任何演员都更好得多 - 他们有更多的钱，更多的人，而且更多的技术致力于这项工作。大男孩出来玩了，他们改变了我们的互联网，通常会更糟。</p><h4>斜坡</h4><p>到目前为止，我提到的因素甚至在Chatgpt和Midjourney和其他生成的AI应用程序之前就已经存在，并在功能中爆炸并广泛使用。现在，产生合理高质量图像和文本的边际成本已接近零。因此，人们正在使用生成的AI用…填充社交媒体。</p><p>博客<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/">垃圾日</a>是我最喜欢的博客之一，它是跟踪互联网模因（另一个是<a href="https://www.infinitescroll.us/">无限滚动</a>）的博客，<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/p/internet-looks-like-now">对此有很好的帖子</a>。这是Facebook的一些图像的图片，其中包括孩子们驾驶塑料瓶的汽车： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg" width="710" height="411.14355231143554" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/feb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:476,&quot;width&quot;:822,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:710,&quot;bytes&quot;:156564,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2